platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: HealthifyMe will change the way you look at weight loss and training. We’ve been blown away by its catalogue of over 20,000 Indian foods, all complete with nutritional information, making it so much easier to track what we eat. Plus, HealthifyMe has over 1,000 fun activities to add to workout routines (including a yoga instructor). Now you can set goals, monitor your progress and slim down at your own pace. Backed by some of India’s top health experts, HealthifyMe has given us the confidence to get our fitness journey started.
